headline: Is UnitedHealth Group a Bargain After 2024 Share Slump and Policy Concerns?
summary: Wondering if UnitedHealth Group is a bargain or a value trap at today’s price? Let us unpack what the market is really implying about this healthcare giant. After a rough stretch that has left the stock down about 32.4% year to date and roughly 28.0% over the last year, shares have shown a short term bounce, gaining around 5.4% in the past week and 6.0% over the last month.
